    "description": "Embark on an exciting Arctic expedition where survival is just the beginning. Lead your group across a rotating map as you scavenge for food, clothing and tools. As mysterious strangers invade the frozen wasteland, your struggle intensifies. Confront external threats and internal conflicts, uncover the fate of lost characters, and survive the relentless Arctic winter as new dangers emerge!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182290/extras/dbf32aba67f4b853330aa5c6fd947c3d.avif?t=1767655590\" width=592 height=93 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182290/extras/94fd599902acca42a5a0517bb697b380.poster.avif?t=1767655590\" width=592 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182290/extras/94fd599902acca42a5a0517bb697b380.webm?t=1767655590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182290/extras/94fd599902acca42a5a0517bb697b380.mp4?t=1767655590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The map changes dynamically with each turn. Your group will face not only a shortage of resources, but also constantly moving ice floes.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Events on the map continuously appear and disappear.<br></li><li>Changing seasons mean mild summers and harsh winters.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182290/extras/99a3ea193d191465e7fce9a579feb78d.avif?t=1767655590\" width=592 height=93 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182290/extras/5546fb7c624a3a600ec91a5f8eda873a.avif?t=1767655590\" width=592 height=223 /></span><br><br>As mysterious strangers appear on the map, uncover their intentions and adapt your strategy. But be prepared — finding the right approach won't always be simple. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182290/extras/daa1416f7be7cf3ea6b496b38f7bff1d.avif?t=1767655590\" width=592 height=93 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182290/extras/ffd44264815210a54419f8b6ddcff4be.poster.avif?t=1767655590\" width=592 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182290/extras/ffd44264815210a54419f8b6ddcff4be.webm?t=1767655590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182290/extras/ffd44264815210a54419f8b6ddcff4be.mp4?t=1767655590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Hunting is crucial for gathering resources. Utilize tools and characters to collect essential supplies in a hunting mini-game. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182290/extras/1f4f016bf882d7acbc93912eb65782e5.avif?t=1767655590\" width=592 height=93 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182290/extras/0e79f96f644e6ba9f0589edf014f9df6.avif?t=1767655590\" width=592 height=223 /></span><br><br>Throughout your journey, you'll meet all kinds of people — some who will stand by you, others who may pose a danger. Build a resilient community to prepare for the arrival of outsiders. Your group is your family and internal conflicts are likely to happen. Immerse yourself in the evolving story of your characters and fight to survive the freezing cold!",
